name: CS156 Machine Learning
tagline: Contains programming and maths homework assignments from Caltech's Machine Learning course CS 156 taught by Professor Yaser Abu-Mostafa. https://work.caltech.edu/telecourse.html
body:
### Welcome!

The repository is updated by me regularly and contains solutions to problem sets in a pdf format (look at `homework-solns` directory) and some code.

Current code implementations include
* Perceptron
* Linear regression
* Non linear transformations for linear regression

### Authors and Contributors
Currently I am the sole contributor to this project @adijo.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
